title: Ep. - 343 - TRISHELLE CANNATELLA FROM THE CHALLENGE: ALL STARS KID 90 REVIEW
description:
Trishelle Cannatella is known for her appearances on the MTV reality television series The Real World: Las Vegas, and the Real World spinoff show The Challenge. She appears in the Paramount Plus new series The Challenge: All Stars, which brings together 22 cast members of the most iconic, boldest, and fiercest challenge all stars from The Real World and Road Rules.

 

Stephen McGee helps Kate review Kid 90,which is an intimate look at young Hollywood starlets growing up in the 1990s, using hundreds of hours of footage captured by Soleil Moon Frye.
